EXTRACT & DATE_PART - To extract specific components of date

Convert column HIRE_DATE (DD/MM/YY format) to Date/Month/Year format

Table Name: Employees
HIRE_DATE
29/08/1999

SELECT DATE PART('DATE', HIRE DATE) as DATE from EMPLOYEES;

Output:
DATE
29

SELECT DATE PART('MONTH', HIRE DATE) as MONTH from EMPLOYEES;
Output:
MONTH
88

SELECT DATE PART('YEAR', HIRE_DATE) as YEAR from EMPLOYEES;
Output:
YEAR
08
